{"tid":1842951,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港人，係呢場疫戰仲可以做乜野？","createTime":"2020-01-26T03:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T07:23:25.000Z","uid":191921,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f8716f6a42ac6398239948cf6e7a420b18209d2b","tid":1842951,"uid":191921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"湖北，北京，上海官宣封城<br />\n大陸各地自斷公路<br />\n嚴格停止大型社交活動<br />\n口罩都要強制帶<br />\n<br />\n香港。。。封城係必要但預左政府無可能做到。<br />\n<br />\n預左初四等班智障返陸狗落到香港會社區大爆發，而家感覺就好似判左死刑再等行刑個下，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兩個字：等死</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最絕望係街邊根本無一半人戴口罩，手更加無可能洗，仲係咁拜年。你自己做盡哂所有野都無用，因身邊有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">太多智障豬隊友</span></strong></span>出去食野買野都夠你中招，最痴線係屋企條渠都播到毒。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">唔想死, 仲有咩可以做！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"30bc68328c3209aa1facdee3463612e224737e79","tid":1842951,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:01:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">繼續抗爭<br />\n加速攬炒<br />\n手足不是Condoms</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a6d33c6f4ff302e87f314e1ed53f9b7980d8aaa","tid":1842951,"uid":182061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:01:43.000Z","msg":"（放負）香港人必須有武漢肺炎未足夠引起支爆嘅心理準備<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1842903\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1842903</a>"},{"pid":"1819b95cfd09f89d004d6325a8410c331c13eeca","tid":1842951,"uid":191921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30bc68328c3209aa1facdee3463612e224737e79","tid":1842951,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:01:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">繼續抗爭<br />\n加速攬炒<br />\n手足不是Condoms</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:02:14.00